title: AMD Ryzen 5 5500 vs Ryzen 5 5600: Which entry-level CPU should you buy?
content:
AMD announced a handful of new Ryzen CPUs as a part of its Spring update. In addition to the more powerful Ryzen 7 5800X3D processor, we also got a couple of relatively less powerful, entry-level chips too. The Ryzen 5 5500 and the Ryzen 5 5600 are the new entry-level processors we got from AMD

The post AMD Ryzen 5 5500 vs Ryzen 5 5600: Which entry-level CPU should you buy? appeared first on xda-developers.
description: In this article, we're going to take a look at the Ryzen 5 5500 vs Ryzen 5 5600 comparison to find out which one's the better CPU to buy.
